Package fr.umlv.Retro

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App  
    AppTest
    Unit test for simple App.
    ClassTransformer
    Retro grade a bytecode from a version to another version by keeping the retro compatibility of the features.
    FileSystem
    Representation of a virtual file system that maintain a reference to opened class files until they are saved on the disk so they can processed multiple times.

    When FileSystem.save() method is called, the class will save the the modified class fields on a sub-directory of the root path.
    Retro
    Facade of the application.
